name: Delicioso - Octoberfest 2021 - Double Toro
additionalNotes: This flavored cigar is a premium cigar with all long filler, aged in above-ground oak barrels set under the sun of the Dominican Island, with natural ingredients. Weeks later, Deliciosos are rolled using a pure Maduro wrapper. Taste elements are that of caramel, citrus, vanilla and malt. Delicioso comes in traditional cigar sizes and a variety of flavors for every cigar smoker.
